text: Giulești may refer to several places in Romania: *Giulești, a neighborhood of Bucharest *Giulești, a commune in Maramureș County *Giulești, a village in Pietroasa Commune, Bihor County *Giulești, a village in Secuieni Commune, Neamț County *Giulești, a village in Boroaia Commune, Suceava County *Giulești and Giuleștii de Sus, villages in Fârtățești Commune, Vâlcea County
